---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Skief Labs" description="Built by someone who learned systems out of necessity. Learn about Skief Labs, founder Sardar Azimov, and our approach to B2B systems.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-linen pt-12 pb-16 md:pt-16 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Text -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="page-hero-title heading-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.8rem] text-navy-900 mb-8 leading-[1.1] uppercase">
            Built by someone who learned systems out of necessity.
          </h1>
          <div class="page-hero-body space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            <p>Skief Labs exists because growing businesses are routinely held together by people doing work that systems should handle.</p>
            <p>Manual follow-ups. Copied data. Unclear ownership. Processes that sort of work — until growth breaks them.</p>
            <p>We've seen this pattern too many times to keep solving it one person at a time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right: Image -->
        <div class="page-hero-image relative">
          <img src="/images/sk7.jpeg" alt="Sardar Azimov" class="w-full rounded-lg object-cover shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_#CFFF15]" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR POINT OF VIEW -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] border-l-4 border-neon pl-4">
            Our point of view
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Most B2B companies don't stall because of bad strategy or bad people.</p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">They stall because their systems never evolved as the business did.</p>
          <p>As teams grow, tools multiply, data fragments, responsibility blurs, and humans quietly become the connective tissue holding everything together. That works — until it becomes fragile.</p>
          <p>Our work is about replacing that fragility with systems that operate reliably — whether or not anyone is watching.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE FOUNDER -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_#CFFF15]">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[40%_60%]">
          <!-- Left: Image -->
          <div class="relative min-h-[400px] md:min-h-[600px]">
            <img src="/images/sk8.jpeg" alt="Sardar Azimov" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/50 to-transparent p-6 md:p-8 pt-16 md:pt-24">
              <p class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-linen tracking-[-0.02em] text-center">Founder & Principal</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Right: Content -->
          <div class="bg-navy-900 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-linen leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] border-l-4 border-neon pl-4 mb-8">
              The Founder
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
              <p>Sardar's background is in business, marketing, and sales — not in engineering or computer science. He learned automation, AI, and systems design out of necessity: building ways to scale commercial output without endlessly hiring or burning teams out. <strong class="text-linen">That origin matters.</strong></p>
              <p>It means every system Skief Labs designs starts with business questions, not technical ones.</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 my-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-neon mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
                  <span>Where is human effort being wasted on work that shouldn't require humans?</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-neon mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
                  <span>Where is risk hiding inside a manual step?</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-neon mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
                  <span>What should stay human — and why?</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-neon mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
                  <span>What should never be automated?</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p class="text-linen font-semibold">Judgment comes before technology. Always.</p>
              <p>Sardar leads every Skief Labs engagement at the architecture level — ensuring solutions stay grounded in business reality rather than technical novelty.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW THE TEAM WORKS -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Heading block -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-block">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy-900"></div>
              <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-navy-900 tracking-[0.2em]">The Studio</p>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 mb-3 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-center">
              How the team works
            </h2>
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy-900"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-10"></div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
          <p class="text-navy-900 text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif italic">
            Skief Labs operates as a studio — deliberately small, deliberately senior.
          </p>
          <p>Projects are architected at a senior level and executed by trusted specialists in data engineering, automation, and AI systems. Every engagement is reviewed for clarity, stability, and ownership before it's delivered.</p>
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-semibold">There are no junior handoffs. No hidden subcontracting. No black boxes.</p>
          <p>Clients always know who is responsible for what — and why decisions are being made.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Callout box -->
        <div class="flex items-stretch gap-4 mt-10">
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy-900 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm italic leading-relaxed py-1 text-left">Every system we deliver is fully documented and handed over — so your team never depends on us to understand what was built or why.</p>
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy-900 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Heading block -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-block">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy-900"></div>
              <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-navy-900 tracking-[0.2em]">The Edge</p>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 mb-3 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-center">
              What makes us different
            </h2>
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy-900"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-10"></div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
          <p>We are not an agency.<br>We are not freelancers.<br>We are not traditional consultants.</p>
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-semibold">We build systems — two specific kinds — with deliberate restraint.</p>
          <p>We work on problems we're genuinely equipped to solve. We don't take on engagements to fill capacity. We say no when something shouldn't be built.</p>
          <p>We document everything so clients never need to come back for something they already paid for.</p>
          <p>We measure success by how little our clients need us over time — not by how much they do.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Callout box -->
        <div class="flex items-stretch gap-4 mt-10">
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy-900 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm italic leading-relaxed py-1 text-left">That last point is the most important one. Dependency is easy to create and profitable to maintain. We've chosen not to.</p>
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy-900 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="cta-box rounded-2xl overflow-hidden grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[38%_62%] bg-navy-900">
        <div class="cta-image-col">
          <img src="/images/sk3.jpg" alt="Discovery call" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center px-8 py-12 md:px-12 md:py-16 text-center">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-[1.75rem] lg:text-[2rem] text-linen mb-4 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]">
            <span class="neon-underline">One entry point. Always the same.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-linen/80 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8 italic">
            A 30-minute discovery call.
          </p>
          <p class="text-linen/60 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Not a pitch. Not a free audit. Not a commitment.
          </p>
          <p class="text-linen/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            A focused conversation to understand where friction is concentrated in your business — and whether we're the right people to remove it.
          </p>
          <p class="text-linen/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
            Either way, you leave the call with more clarity than you arrived with.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-book-btn btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              Book a 30-minute discovery call
              <span class="cta-arrow text-lg inline-block transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
            </a>
            <p class="text-linen/50 text-sm italic">No pitch. No obligation. Just clarity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
